project.title: Final Project: Pickup
project.subtitle: Boot Camp final project. React, Java, Spring
project.content: Basic functionality: posting new orders, drivers being able to accept orders, and connecting backend to separate React frontend. The primary goal of this project is to gain familiarity building React front end projects, and linking them to our Java Spring MVC backend.
